  2470	            with the DDN Network Security Officer.  The SCC also
  2471	            distributes the DDN Security Bulletin, which communicates
  2472	            information on network and host security exposures, fixes,
  2473	            and concerns to security and management personnel at DDN
  2474	            facilities.  It is available online, via kermit or anonymous
