  2477	            number).  The SCC provides immediate assistance with DDN-
  2478	            related host security problems; call (800) 235-3155 (6:00
  2479	            a.m. to 5:00 p.m. Pacific Time) or send email to
  2480	            SCC@NIC.DDN.MIL.  For 24 hour coverage, call the MILNET
