  2559	            Formed in August of 1989, the team has a constituency that
  2560	            is primarily Ames users, but it is also involved in
  2561	            assisting other NASA Centers and federal agencies.  CNSRT
  2562	            maintains liaisons with the DOE's CIAC team and the DARPA
  2563	            CERT.  It is also a charter member of the CERT System.  The
  2564	            team may be reached by 24 hour pager at (415) 694-0571, or
  2565	            by electronic mail to CNSRT@AMES.ARC.NASA.GOV.
