  4957	           Electronic Information", OTA-CIT-310, October 1987.
  4958	
  4959	           This report, prepared for congressional committee considering
  4960	           Federal policy on the protection of electronic information, is
  4961	           interesting because of the issues it raises regarding the
  4962	           impact of technology used to protect information.  It also
  4963	           serves as a reasonable introduction to the various encryption
  4964	           and information protection mechanisms.  185 pages.  Available
  4965	           from the U.S. Government Printing Office.
  4966	
  4967	   [PALMER]
