  4973	           Englewood Cliffs, NJ, 1989.
  4974	
  4975	           A general textbook in computer security, this book provides an
  4976	           excellent and very readable introduction to classic computer
  4977	
  4978	
  4979	
  4980	Site Security Policy Handbook Working Group                    [Page 89]
