  4982	RFC 1244                 Site Security Handbook                July 1991
  4983	
  4984	
  4985	           security problems and solutions, with a particular emphasis on
  4986	           encryption.  The encryption coverage serves as a good
  4987	           introduction to the subject.  Other topics covered include
  4988	           building secure programs and systems, security of database,
  4989	           personal computer security, network and communications
  4990	           security, physical security, risk analysis and security
  4991	           planning, and legal and ethical issues.  538 pages including
  4992	           index and bibliography.
