  5236	           This 36 page report (GAO/IMTEC-89-57), by the U.S.
  5237	           Government Accounting Office, describes the Internet worm
  5238	           and its effects.  It gives a good overview of the various
  5239	           U.S. agencies involved in the Internet today and their
